The resource consumption objectives for the component are defined in the SWA in Component Diagram "SW Architecture" at the following location in Enterprise Architect:
VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.SomeIP.SW Architecture.Components.Estimated Resource Consumption Cdd_SOMEIP

Performance: The performance objectives are defined in the SWA - see [Performance Objectives]. Memory Consumption: The memory consumption objectives are defined in the SWA - see [Memory Consumption Objectives]. CPU Load: The CPU load objectives are defined in the SWA - see [CPU Load Objectives].
